{"tid":2061722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"減少濕疹 發作嘅最有效方法","createTime":"2020-06-12T14:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T04:54:07.000Z","uid":336730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f49da38ce95bd954ee15ae7715dd9ae9b23c4741","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"1.有啲人話 戎咗牛濕疹就冇晒<br />\n<br />\n2.有啲人話 搬咗去外國住濕疹消失<br />\n<br />\n3.有啲人話 細個有 大個冇晒<br />\n<br />\n以上3個成功例子 只不過係代表佢地遠離咗致敏源，每個濕疹嘅人致敏源都唔同 有啲人可能有10樣野接觸到會過敏<br />\n<br />\n所以100%100%必定係去驗血 去測試下你致敏源係咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你有濕疹係代表你日日係度接觸緊致敏源 ，而且係嚴重過敏，而有啲致敏源避唔到 但可以減少接觸，咁你痕嘅程度就會大大減少<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n人會乾 會痕 會甩皮係受食物 同 環境影響，你可能對大豆嚴重過敏而成日食大豆 所以由細到大都有濕疹。你又有可能對花粉嚴重過敏，而你住緊嘅地方好近大自然，有一日搬咗屋 你嘅濕疹消失晒！又有啲人係超敏嬰兒 對 大豆 奶 蛋過敏 日日食攪到皮膚有濕疹，一戎口 即贏好返。而啲濕鳩皮膚科醫生淨係開藥唔叫你去驗血係想你個個月去<br />\n覆診交錢養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n          我有個朋友由細到大都有濕疹，就算食咗類固醇 止痕藥 都會痕痕地，一食晒啲藥就係咁爆發出黎，之後去驗血 原來係對大豆嚴重過敏，市面上勁多野食都有大豆成份eg 9成拉面湯底一定有 朱古力一定有 雞粉一定有 ，攪到乜都食唔到，但可以食牛 蝦 同蟹 食完冇事！戎完大豆之後晚晚有教好瞓 但基於要出街食飯難避味精 所以都有起返濕疹，但程度遠少於之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebee764d71dbfe27293179bf994b3bd2d506ff63","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n早兩個月又翻發 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00de48ba2cbb8ecce56078c8a0c0a4ee85ea30c","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebee764d71dbfe27293179bf994b3bd2d506ff63","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n早兩個月又翻發 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"濕疹係你食到致敏源 或者接觸到致敏源 先出現<br />\n<br />\n有啲人驗血驗20種最常接觸到嘅致敏源就搵到兇手，但有啲人要驗300種 先搵到，所以病情嚴重嘅人要選擇驗最多種致敏源嘅plan"},{"pid":"f68aa89c43eabe1c208b08d108bf20263a97cc66","tid":2061722,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"多謝分享"},{"pid":"b2a3d533fdb39cc81895875d9830549b12b04ffd","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00de48ba2cbb8ecce56078c8a0c0a4ee85ea30c","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebee764d71dbfe27293179bf994b3bd2d506ff63","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n早兩個月又翻發 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"濕疹係你食到致敏源 或者接觸到致敏源 先出現<br />\n<br />\n有啲人驗血驗20種最常接觸到嘅致敏源就搵到兇手，但有啲人要驗300種 先搵到，所以病情嚴重嘅人要選擇驗最多種致敏源嘅plan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"可以去邊度驗？<br />\n會唔會好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195856276af7e7ecda56d09cc010e09aefc85a70","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2a3d533fdb39cc81895875d9830549b12b04ffd","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00de48ba2cbb8ecce56078c8a0c0a4ee85ea30c","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebee764d71dbfe27293179bf994b3bd2d506ff63","tid":2061722,"uid":305954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n早兩個月又翻發 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"濕疹係你食到致敏源 或者接觸到致敏源 先出現<br />\n<br />\n有啲人驗血驗20種最常接觸到嘅致敏源就搵到兇手，但有啲人要驗300種 先搵到，所以病情嚴重嘅人要選擇驗最多種致敏源嘅plan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"可以去邊度驗？<br />\n會唔會好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://meddx.com.hk/fast-check.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmeddx.com.hk%2Ffast-check.html&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=1c111fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://meddx.com.hk/fast-check.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我朋友去依間，選擇咗最平嘅plan ，戒完大豆之後起碼唔會狂甩皮，小紅小痕就有嘅 <br />\n<br />\n致敏源可以係千奇百怪 ，驗咗唔一定甩晒，但對個病情一定大大有幫助"},{"pid":"72ac1f60f3299043c6f72e73c4c90e63aa408e13","tid":2061722,"uid":150293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"空氣清新機有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad858e6a1b8ca0c15a47c4e60d3717766c3ef1ac","tid":2061722,"uid":336730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ac1f60f3299043c6f72e73c4c90e63aa408e13","tid":2061722,"uid":150293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"空氣清新機有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"人對每種物質都有保護罩，取決厚定簿。有人對霉菌 嚴重過敏就有用 你可能冇 買黎或者浪費咗啲錢 去驗血就知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家日日接觸 /進食致敏源 之後搽藥膏係治標不治本，啲藥膏只不過係舒緩你啲症狀  解決唔到你啲致敏源"},{"pid":"233ccdad0ab25941eabbd5fd19abb10b187a9bff","tid":2061722,"uid":213496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T18:04:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"56e9c147aa17c293115f55b0c58feda266c09429","tid":2061722,"uid":143735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"屋企養貓 對貓敏感可以點？。。"},{"pid":"f8330794a07fda034c9669cbb32535af3c806f48","tid":2061722,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,